title: Fear for Sale: The Dusk Wanderer Collector's Edition
description: EleFun Games proudly presents the newest addition to the Fear For Sale series! It's been 40 years since a young couple disappeared in the European countryside. The case went cold until the missing woman was seen in her childhood home having seemingly not aged a day! What starts as a normal investigation quickly takes a dark turn as dark spirits try to stand in your way. Can you uncover what happened to the couple, or will you get lost in a labyrinth of mystery and deceit? Find out in this thrilling hidden-object puzzle adventure!
